```

## Conventions

- Services as ViewModels with `BehaviorSubject` for state
- Selectors as derived observables with `pipe(map(...))`
- `switchMap` for requests that cancel the previous one
- `shareReplay(1)` to avoid re-execution
- `catchError` on every HTTP observable
- `distinctUntilChanged` to avoid duplicate emissions
- Private `updateState` method for immutable updates
